Borodino - Wehrmacht Equipment

The SS division "Das Reich" and parts of the 10th Panzer Division approached the battlefield near Borodino 100 km west of Moscow. Between them and the Russian capital there stood the over-strengthened 32nd Siberian Infantry Division which had just arrived by train to complete a part of the Mozhaisk defense line. After five days of brutal fighting the SS division achieved a victory but the formerly fresh troops just felt as survivors ...

